9. Conclusion

This project demonstrates an end-to-end data engineering workflow:

* Ingesting raw data
* Cleaning and validating it
* Building analytical models
* Delivering actionable insights through a dashboard

It reflects real-world data warehouse design and is suitable for both **academic learning and portfolio demonstration**.
